Description.Chinese: 将货物获得所有港动效果的几率提高到 100%。这意味着在每次被动交易中，您将从提到的商品池中随机选择一件商品。
Description.English: Increases the chance for goods for all Harbour Activity Effects to 100%. This means on each passive trade you will get one randomly choosen good from the mentioned goodspool.
